      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car looking for its next owner. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it\u2019s an affordable way into motoring for someone who wants a cheap runabout, a learner car, or a straightforward project to tinker with. If you\u2019re handy with cars or just need something budget-friendly with potential, this could be a great fit. Priced to sell and described honestly.",
