      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with good bones and a strong, straightforward mechanical layout. It shows age cosmetically and will benefit from TLC, but it fires up, moves out well, and offers the kind of simple, serviceable platform that\u2019s getting harder to find. A great option for someone who wants affordable transportation, a weekend fixer, or a practical base for gradual restoration.",
