    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Here\u2019s a chance to pick up a car with real personality at an approachable price. It\u2019s not pretending to be showroom-perfect\u2014this is the kind of vehicle for someone who appreciates honest metal, everyday usefulness, and the satisfaction of bringing out its next chapter. Whether you need affordable wheels, a practical backup, or a project with promise, this one has the kind of presence that invites a little vision and rewards the right owner. A straightforward, budget-conscious opportunity with plenty of potential.",
      "price": 5900.0,
