      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle offers an affordable entry point for a buyer looking for straightforward transportation. Priced to move, it presents a practical opportunity for someone who values low upfront cost and room to make it their own. A sensible choice for commuting, errands, or a project-minded owner seeking value.",
