      "description": "Solid budget-friendly ride that\u2019s perfect for someone who wants dependable basic transportation without spending a fortune. It\u2019s not a showroom car, but it\u2019s a great option for a commuter, first car, or handy buyer looking for something affordable with plenty of life left to give. Priced fairly and represented honestly by a seller who believes in being straight with people.",
